    <title>搭建一个属于自己的图床</title>
    <link href="https://blog.morino.top/2024/11/05/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/"/>
    <id>https://blog.morino.top/2024/11/05/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/</id>
    <published>2024-11-05T12:20:29.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-11-11T07:16:18.479Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="一、购买阿里云或其他OSS资源"><a href="#一、购买阿里云或其他OSS资源" class="headerlink" title="一、购买阿里云或其他OSS资源"></a>一、购买阿里云或其他OSS资源</h3><p>因为我自己使用的是阿里云服务，所以下面使用的是阿里云OSS服务。<br>登录阿里云账号，搜索框搜索 <code>对象存储OSS</code> 。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111409224.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111409224.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111140934193"></p><p>点击立即购买，选择适合自己的产品。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111410924.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111410924.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141027874"></p><p>付款成功后进入控制台。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111411203.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111411203.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141138121"></p><h3 id="二、配置OSS"><a href="#二、配置OSS" class="headerlink" title="二、配置OSS"></a>二、配置OSS</h3><h4 id="1、创建Bucket"><a href="#1、创建Bucket" class="headerlink" title="1、创建Bucket"></a>1、创建Bucket</h4><p>在界面的右侧中间有Bucket管理选项，创建新的Bucket，取一个自己喜欢的名字。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111412185.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111412185.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141209153"></p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111412593.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111412593.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141229535"></p><h4 id="2、获取AccessKey"><a href="#2、获取AccessKey" class="headerlink" title="2、获取AccessKey"></a>2、获取AccessKey</h4><p>将鼠标放到右上角头像处，选择AccessKey。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111413914.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111413914.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141308882"></p><p>创建子用户AccessKey。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111413432.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111413432.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141336406"></p><p>点击创建用户后进入如下界面后设置登录名称，访问方式全选后保持默认就好。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111414302.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111414302.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141416256"></p><p>确定后，子用户创立成功，记得保存AccessKey ID和AccessKey Secret，关闭页面后无法再次获取到这两个数据，后面还会用到。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111415280.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111415280.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141510238"></p><p>点击用户登录名称，进入用户管理界面，增加权限 AliyunOSSFullAccess 和 AliyunOSSReadOnlyAccess 。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111415097.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111415097.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141556046"></p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111416361.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111416361.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141614319"></p><h4 id="3、为Bucket增加授权"><a href="#3、为Bucket增加授权" class="headerlink" title="3、为Bucket增加授权"></a>3、为Bucket增加授权</h4><p>回到Bucket管理界面，为其增加刚刚建立的子用户的授权。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111417105.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111417105.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141709035"></p><h3 id="三、配置PicGO"><a href="#三、配置PicGO" class="headerlink" title="三、配置PicGO"></a>三、配置PicGO</h3><p>下载[picgo安装包](<a href="https://github.com/Molunerfinn/PicGo/releases">Releases · Molunerfinn&#x2F;PicGo</a>)。</p><p>安装好后进入如下界面，配置名可随意填写，KeyID和Key Secret就直接填AccessKey ID和AccessKey Secret，Bucket填写刚创建的Bucket的名称，存储区域在<a href="https://help.aliyun.com/zh/oss/user-guide/regions-and-endpoints?spm=a2c4g.11174283.0.0.74077368LpmsAu">OSS地域和访问域名_对象存储(OSS)-阿里云帮助中心</a>中查找自己所购的OSS服务的<strong>OSS专用地域ID</strong>。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111419997.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111419997.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111141912969"></p><p>配置好后，可以上传图片进行试验，如果报错可根据报错在网上寻找解决的方法。</p><h3 id="四、配置Typora"><a href="#四、配置Typora" class="headerlink" title="四、配置Typora"></a>四、配置Typora</h3><p>安装好Typora后打开设置界面，选择图像，当插入图片时上传图像，下面选择Picgo并指定Picgo的安装路径。</p><p><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111420863.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111420863.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111142026821">配置完成后点击验证图片上传选项，出现如下界面则代表成功绑定。<br><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111421530.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111421530.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111142114505"></p><h3 id="PS"><a href="#PS" class="headerlink" title="PS"></a>PS</h3><p>如果想将图片放在博客中使用或以其他方式供其他人访问，则需关闭阻止公共访问，并设置成公共可读。<br><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111425421.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111425421.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111142513383"><br><img src="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111426858.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://morino-images.oss-ap-southeast-1.aliyuncs.com/202411111426858.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="image-20241111142619815"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
